INSERT INTO `review_detail` VALUES (1,1,1,'1-dozen beautiful strawberries!!!','These were amazing!!! Super fresh, beautiful, and delicious! Your timely delivery and process are definitely the best around!!!!','Wendy',NULL),(2,2,1,'Made a 10 year old very happy','Since I couldn\'t spend my Godchild\'s double-digit birthday with her. I thought she would enjoy this surprise. And boy was it a success.','Edna',NULL),(3,3,1,'Birthday gift!','I sent 2 dozen gourmet dipped strawberries to my daughter for her birthday. She raved about how large and juicy and flavorful the strawberries were. Thank you for making her day.','Karen',NULL),(4,4,1,'No Complaints','Got these last min for my beaus birthday. Arrived on time. Along with balloons and a teddy. Thank you!','Denesha',NULL),(5,5,1,'Yummy','I purchased this for my wife and she ate them in a day. What a product. Love it.','Elbert',NULL),(6,6,1,'Valentines present','The first page of strawberries was not delivered in a sealed container as they usually are. Upon complaining I was told a new pig of strawberries would be delivered on 2/17 before 8 pm. They were never delivered.','Stanley',NULL),(7,7,1,'Valentine gifts','I always send Sherri’s Berry’s to my Grandchildren for Valentine’s Day. They love them!!\r\nI can always count on them to be delivered fresh and right on time!!','Suzanne',NULL),(8,8,1,'Wonderful','Delivery was above and beyond, very professional, and awesome. The product was beautiful and very well presented also tasty and delicious bravo! Rated 1-10 10 being the best rating it was definitely a 10!','Gregory',NULL),(9,9,1,'Amazing','They were so delicious. I ordered 2 more','Taejah',NULL),(10,10,1,'Arrived As Shown & Delicious!','The title says it all and my wife and daughter loved them. That\'s all that matters to me. Thank you Shari\'s Berries.','Daniel',NULL),(11,11,1,'Chocolate wonders','I sent this item as a birthday gift to a lady who was just\r\nentering Social Security age. She opened it, slightly depressed at all the years, and was suddenly delighted to see her two favorite tastes: strawberries and chocolate.\r\nShe enters the next chapter in her life a happy senior!','Stanley',NULL),(12,12,1,'Berries for our Friends','Our friends who received them thought they were incredibly tasty. They absolutely loved them!!! ','Candy',NULL),(13,13,1,'The best !','Love this place, love the arrangements, the taste, the quickness, and the company overall. Will continue to order :)','Mary',NULL),(14,14,1,'Strawberry gift','This was a gift so I don\'t know what they actually looked like but we have received and given these in the past and were already happy. The gift recipient was very pleased. Said they were delicious.','Stuart',NULL),(15,15,1,'Loved Them','I sent it to a friend for her birthday. She loved them but didn’t realize they were Champagne chocolate. A little bit high for just 12 and shipping.','Robin',NULL),(16,16,1,'Strawberries','Absolutely love them! They came exactly when they were supposed to.','Keith',NULL),(17,17,1,'Top Shelf','My girlfriend was taken away by the dessert. She had mentioned she wanted a champagne-flavored wedding cake a while back and this lit her face up. Thank you!','John',NULL),(18,18,1,'Rainy Day','This cold rainy day in Mississippi, my box has arrived. Laidback on my chaise with a warm cozy throw blanket and my delicious berries. What a Friday! ','Yolanda',NULL),(19,19,1,'The best EVER','These were absolutely AMAZING. Great size and beautifully presented.','Margaret',NULL),(20,20,1,'Birthday gift','My mom loved her birthday gift, she raved about how delicious the strawberries were. I was notified when strawberries were delivered which I really appreciated!','Kalundra',NULL),(21,21,1,'Perfect','Everything went off well and the recipients loved them!!!!','Matthew',NULL),(22,22,1,'Delivery was on time','Was sent as a birthday gift, granddaughter loved it','Marilyn',NULL),(23,23,1,'Birthday Strawberries','The strawberries were excellent. They were fresh and delicious. Birthday mom was thrilled with her gift.','Frank',NULL),(24,24,1,'Wow','It was a birthday celebration and she loves it ','Marta',NULL),(25,25,1,'She loved ❤️ ... them !!!','They were absolutely beautiful !!! They were packaged perfectly !!! And she said it was the best gift !!! Ever !!!!!','Kathleen',NULL),(26,26,1,'They where for my Girlfriend ...','Not too hard to order and for me, that\'s what I need.\r\nShe was astonished and that\'s all that matters.\r\nHopefully, they can do a time delivery option soon...','Rick',NULL),(27,27,1,'Absolutely delicious','A perfect mid-winter pick me up. My daughter and I enjoyed them. Dark chocolate is my favorite.','Kathy',NULL),(28,28,1,'Dark chocolate perfect for dairy issues','Still enjoying the pleasure without the dairy issues.','Leslie',NULL),(29,29,1,'Great !','These were a gift and very well received. They lived them!','Patricis',NULL),(30,30,1,'Perfect Christmas Gift !!!','DELICIOUS chocolate-covered strawberries! Delivered on time, great service. Would definitely order again.','Mary',NULL),(31,31,1,'Great Strawberries','Really juicy big strawberries.','Kathy',NULL),(32,32,1,'Any occasion','It was something special for a special person in my life. She said they were delicious thank you.','Edward',NULL),(33,33,1,'Perfect, As Usual','My order came a day early, which was great because I ordered them a day late. The packaging was perfect, the strawberries were large, juicy, and delicious. And the entire berries were dipped, as opposed to other vendors, who only dip half. Will definitely order again.','Pamela',NULL),(34,34,1,'Delicious berries','Always great!! The shipping is a little pricey!','Barbara',NULL),(35,35,1,'Loved it','My family member loves their birthday gift. They were so happy to receive them.','Cassandra',NULL),(36,36,1,'Good stuff !','Probably one of the best chocolate-covered strawberries we\'ve had. I think it just felt/tasted unique with the \"glitter\" and the crunch, especially when they are freshly cold out of the fridge. Made my wife very happy. Good stuff!','Matthew',NULL),(37,37,1,'Impressed','Yes, the gift recipient was very impressed not only by the beautiful look of the strawberries but of the taste. They said they were delicious. They couldn’t stop thanking me for the gift.','Ann',NULL),(38,38,1,'Just what I ordered','The order was great but I didn’t know at the time was my wife wanted chocolate-covered strawberries ','Daniel',NULL),(39,39,1,'BEST STRAWBERRIES ','If you want to impress a loved one with the best strawberries ever try these. These strawberries are such a delicious delight. My family absolutely loves them.','Gemyse',NULL),(40,40,1,'Perfect Gift !','Perfect Gift! Send these berries as a congratulations gift and it’s fit them well. Definitely recommend!','Chase',NULL),(41,41,1,'Amazing','My daughter absolutely loved them they were fresh and such amazing colors. Perfect for her Unicorn Birthday theme 5th party she was so excited when she received them!!!!!','Nyla',NULL),(42,42,1,'Best chocolate coveredstrawberries','Great strawberries. Tastes great. Looks even tastier and wonderful.','Bevin',NULL),(43,43,1,'Great present for someone','Very unusual and delicious present to someone. Tastes great.\r\nHighly recommend.','Svetlana',NULL),(44,44,1,'Super Birthday Gift to my Mom!','She LOVED these beautifully decorated and fresh strawberries! Thank you for helping me celebrate her in a special way!','Felicia',NULL),(45,45,1,'Delicious Delights!','On time is always nice but ahead of time is even better for delivery expectations.\r\nThese strawberries where for our daughter’s 17th birthday. Every. Single. Berry. Was perfect !!!','Dee',NULL),(46,46,1,'Great edible gift','The person I bought these for was extremely happy and satisfied with the size and quality of the strawberries. I had heard that the berries from Sheri berries were the best. These make easy thoughtful gifts that won\'t take up space for long and can be shared.','Guillermo',NULL),(47,47,1,'Pleasant Surprise!','The white chocolate-covered strawberries were truly a pleasant surprise! They were yummy as well!! What a wonderful birthday present!','Jerry',NULL),(48,48,1,'Delicious!','I order Shari’s berries just because they’re so good! The delivery driver is so nice and friendly. Shari’s berries are so good! ','Tiffany',NULL),(49,49,1,'Strawberry\'s','My daughter loves them and big they were. Thank you so much. This put a big smile on her face.','Theresa',NULL),(50,50,1,'Perfect','Fresh and delicious. My wife loved them.','Alexander',NULL),(51,51,1,'Beautiful','They came fresh and delicious. My wife loved them. She always wanted to try Sheri\'s Berries and she was glad we did.','Ihkand',NULL),(52,52,1,'On Time, Fresh & Delicious...','Actually, that is my review. The berries were delivered on time. They were fresh. And they were delicious. Thanks for making my wife\'s Valentine\'s Day sweets a success!','Alexander',NULL),(53,53,1,'Excellent !','The strawberries were on time snd were beautiful. Not to mention, very nice big berries. And good as always.','Cindy',NULL),(54,54,1,'Always A Great Gift','Strawberries were delivered as promised and were well presented. Taste great as well!!!!','Greg',NULL),(55,55,1,'Great size and presentation','The person receiving this as the gift was very impressed. Ate half of them on the first day. Delicious and great size.','Alisa',NULL),(56,56,1,'Great berried','My granddaughter loved the dipped berries I sent her.','Marjory',NULL),(57,57,1,'Dipped Strawberries','I loved them they were perfect and I will shop with you guys again thank you ❤️✨','Laniya',NULL),(58,58,1,'Delicious','The berries were fresh, juicy and the chocolate was thick and plentiful!\r\nA truly delicious treat!','Marry',NULL),(59,59,1,'PERFECT GIFT','I sent this to a friend who did a tremendous favor for me, she loved the berries!','Sue',NULL),(60,60,1,'Best Berries','These were a gift for my son-in-laws birthday, as always, Edible Blooms did not disappoint!','Brigitte',NULL),(61,61,1,'Sweet Smiles','How can you not have a good experience? Delivery was prompt and flexible. The strawberry smiles were perfect in every way. Thank you all involved in the process for adding a little extra joy to our day!','Erin',NULL),(62,62,1,'Berries','The berries were very fresh and delicious.','Margery',NULL),(63,63,1,'Great Gift','The box of Chocolate covered Strawberries was outstanding.','Crsar',NULL),(64,64,1,'Strawberry Smiles','These were a gift to my sister after a medical event. The smiles cheered her up and she enjoyed the delicious berries!','Anthony',NULL),(65,65,1,'Smiley Berries','Bought the mixed smiley berries and they brought smiles. That\'s what I hoped the reaction would be!','Andrew',NULL),(66,66,1,'Strawberry Smiles','These berries were a gift to my daughter-in-law who is recovering from an illness. She loved the smiley faces! Chocolate is always good medicine. The berries were delicious and arrived right on time when you said they would. Thank you!','Betty',NULL),(67,67,1,'Chocolate Strawberries','My girl really liked the chocolate strawberries. Everything went well with the delivery and everything. I will be using you again and thanks I was more than satisfied. Thank you so much!','James',NULL),(68,68,1,'Nice Shades','The colors were unique and beautifull.','Louanne',NULL),(69,69,1,'Unicorn Magic','Delightfully colorful sparkly strawberries! What a perfect treat to send to my daughters! Thank you for always bringing joy to them!','Jeannette',NULL),(70,70,1,'Mother\'s Day','Mother\'s day gift. My wife thought they were beautiful and delicious!','Drnnis',NULL);
